data.description: Beautiful brick rancher nestled in the desirable neighborhood of Aberdeen. This home boosts great curb appeal as you drive up. Step inside to a large open living room, kitchen area with granite counters, plenty of cabinets for storage with soft close cabinets, stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar. Just off the living room is a nice formal dining room with a wood burning fireplace between living and dining room. Down the hall you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms.  Off the living room is a bonus sunroom with a fireplace, fans etc.  Enjoy the outdoor/indoor living.  Basement offers a large family room, wet bar and additional area for either game room, kids area and so forth. Additional bedroom and bathroom too. Schedule your showings today to view this beautiful home.
